# Output Directory

This directory contains all generated visualizations, reports, and analysis outputs from the Movie Rating Analysis project.

## Generated Files

- `01_rating_analysis.png` - Rating distribution, trends, and box plots
- `02_genre_analysis.png` - Genre analysis visualizations
- `analysis_report.txt` - Comprehensive text report
- Other analysis outputs will be saved here

All files are automatically generated when running the analysis.
